    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, You have touched me and You have shown me"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That I am not so simple as I thought."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I often run and hide, prone to an errant heart."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But there is not a pause and You pursue!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And behold You’ve caught me altogether!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Where can I go from Your Spirit, O Lord?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I can’t flee from Your presence, You’re inside me."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I’ve climbed the steep mountains, but You still are there,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Descend to the valleys but You find me."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now I see, there’s something more to this pattern:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You want to show me all that You are."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So You’ve drawn me from this strife, into the family life."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As one, our prayers can match Your deep desires."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now behold we follow You together!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
